captions.text: Just what do you think you're doing?

I thought we were trying to escape
certain death!

Tell me if my memory is incorrect,
Elizabeth...
but weren't you and I about to be married??
You sure picked a fine time to show me your having second thoughts!
What was all that, "I've been searching the world just to find you" business??
It look like the one that once did the wanting suddenly wants to
be wanted by a different wanting that has a want to
wanting that has never been wanted for the sake of wanted-ness.
I was actually just trying to distract him so I could handcuff him to the mast.
I wanted to chain him up as bait.
Hey wait just one moment there, love.
That doesn't help me out in the slightest.
I can't believe I thought I knew you!
Will, I was doing it for us!
I mean, we were in love!
it's as if someone just completely rewrote your characteristics

"pointless drama" regardless of everything
you've ever said or did before this point.
I actually was trying to get her in the sack.
I only wanted to stab Jack in the back when I discovered he had selfish reasons for helping me find you..
But mostly to save your own skin, correct?
From this point on, I'm out.

This isn't anything like the ride
at Disney World!
Ah, hello there, sir! I believe you have my locker.
